body.name: HONEY JOY Baby Stroller, Foldable High Landscape Infant Carriage with Foot Cover, Adjustable Backrest & Canopy, Suspension Wheels & Storage Basket, Newborn Pushchair Stroller for Boys Girls (Black)
features: 【High-view Stroller with Foot Cover】Our high landscape baby stroller is designed with a suitable seat height of 19.5", which enables babies to enjoy nature from a broader view. Besides, an additional foot cover will effectively keep babies away from car exhaust pollution while letting them stay warm in cold weather.

【Adjustable Canopy & Backrest】3-section canopy can be adjusted freely according to the weather conditions. The panoramic skylight on the canopy makes it convenient to observe baby's every move. Additionally, the backrest and footrest can also be adjusted to different angles, to meet baby's requirements like sitting, semi-reclining or sleeping.

【Quick Folding for Easy Carrying】With one-touch folding button, you can quickly fold the stroller. The built-in hook securely locks the whole frame, allowing you to carry the stroller without hidden dangers. Measuring 33.5" x 22.5" x 14.5" when folded, the compact stroller fits perfectly into your car trunk for traveling.

【Quality Frame & Practical Design】Framed by heavy-duty steel, the pram is sturdy for baby aged from 0 to 36 months to use. Padded seat with 5-point safety harness lets the baby sit comfortably and safely inside. With a cup holder, a zippered pocket and a bottom storage basket, you can keep baby's supplies within reach.

【Designed for Smooth Strolling】Premium EVA wheels have excellent anti-slip and shock-absorbed performance, ensuring that the stroller rides smoothly on all daily terrain roads. Even better, the front wheels can be rotated 360°for flexible control and the rear wheels with one-step brake system work for emergency stops.
body.description: Description:Traveling with a newborn or growing baby just got easier with our High-Landscape Strollers. The infant stroller with foot cover enables the baby to enjoy the outside world from a wide vision while avoiding car exhaust pollution. The adjustable canopy and backrest allow your baby to sit or lie down as he pleases. And a 5-point safety belt keeps your baby safe. In addition, there is a cup holder and a storage basket for convenient storage of outings. Designed with non-slip and shock-absorbed wheels, the stroller can ride smoothly on any road. When not in use, simply press the one-touch fold button to easily fold the stroller.Feature:High-landscape stroller allows babies to see the outside from a wider viewDetachable foot cover keeps baby warm while blocking exhaust pollution4-section awning with skylight for easy observation of baby's every moveAdjustable backrest and footrest meet baby's sitting or semi-lying needsOne-touch folding stroller folds quickly for convenient storage or travelingPremium steel frame pram accompanies baby's growth from 0-36 monthsPadded large seat with 5-point safety harness ensures comfort and safetyShock-resistant EVA tires provide a smooth strolling on any terrain roadsRotating front wheels for control, One-step brake rear wheels for parkingCup holder, storage basket & zippered pocket make baby items accessibleSpecifications: Color: Black/GrayMaterial: Steel, EVA, Linen, 300D PolyesterProduct Dimension: 22.5" x 36" x 42" (L x W x H) Folding Dimension: 33.5" x 22.5" x 14.5" (L x W x H) Net Weight: 20 lbsWeight Capacity of Baby Stroller: 33 lbsWeight Capacity of Mesh Basket: 4.5 lbsSuitable Age: 0-36 MonthsPackage Includes：1 x Baby Stroller1 x User's Manual
